<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Support Center</h1>

  <div class="prose lg:prose-xl max-w-4xl mb-10">
    <p class="text-xl mb-8">Need help using Genderbase? We're here to assist you with any questions or issues you might encounter.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
    <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-6 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
      <p class="mb-6">Find quick answers to common questions about using our platform.</p>
      <a href="#faq" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto">View FAQs</a>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-6 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-secondary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Contact Support</h3>
      <p class="mb-6">Need personalized help? Our support team is ready to assist you.</p>
      <a href="#contact-form" class="btn btn-secondary mt-auto">Contact Us</a>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-6 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">User Guides</h3>
      <p class="mb-6">Browse our detailed guides on how to use Genderbase effectively.</p>
      <a href="#guides" class="btn btn-accent mt-auto">View Guides</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="faq" class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-200 mb-4">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-medium">
          How do I create an account?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content">
          <p>To create an account, click the "Sign Up" button in the top right corner of any page. Fill out the registration form with your email address and create a password. You'll receive a confirmation email to verify your account before you can start using all features.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-200 mb-4">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-medium">
          How do I ask a question?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content">
          <p>To ask a question, navigate to the "Ask a Question" page from the main navigation menu. Fill out the question form with as much detail as possible. Our volunteer responders will review your question and provide an answer typically within 24-48 hours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-200 mb-4">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-medium">
          Can I contribute content to Genderbase?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content">
          <p>Yes! We welcome community contributions. You can contribute articles, resources, or answers to questions. To get started, visit the "Contribute" section under the "Community" menu. All contributions go through a review process to ensure accuracy and quality.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-200 mb-4">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-medium">
          How do I search for specific topics?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content">
          <p>Use the search bar at the top of any page to find content related to specific topics. You can also browse our Knowledge Base and filter by categories or tags to find information on particular subjects.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-200 mb-4">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-medium">
          Is my information kept private?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content">
          <p>Yes, we take privacy seriously. Your personal information is protected and never shared with third parties. You can ask questions anonymously if you prefer. For more details, please review our <a href="<%= home_privacy_path %>" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="contact-form" class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-8 mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Contact Support</h2>

    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <form class="space-y-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">Your Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="w-full input input-bordered" placeholder="Enter your name">
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">Email Address</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="w-full input input-bordered" placeholder="Enter your email">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="subject" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">Subject</label>
          <select id="subject" name="subject" class="w-full select select-bordered">
            <option value="" selected disabled>Select a topic</option>
            <option value="account">Account Issues</option>
            <option value="questions">Asking or Answering Questions</option>
            <option value="technical">Technical Problems</option>
            <option value="content">Content Concerns</option>
            <option value="other">Other</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" class="w-full textarea textarea-bordered" placeholder="Describe your issue or question in detail"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Submit Support Request</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="guides" class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">User Guides</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-40 bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Getting Started Guide</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Learn the basics of creating an account and navigating Genderbase.</p>
          <a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline">Read Guide →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-40 bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-secondary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Asking Effective Questions</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Tips for formulating questions that get helpful, accurate answers.</p>
          <a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline">Read Guide →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-40 bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Using the Knowledge Base</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">How to effectively search and navigate our knowledge resources.</p>
          <a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline">Read Guide →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-40 bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Contributing Content</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Guidelines for submitting articles and resources to our platform.</p>
          <a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline">Read Guide →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-40 bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-secondary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Privacy & Security</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Understanding our privacy features and how to keep your account secure.</p>
          <a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline">Read Guide →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-40 bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Community Guidelines</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Our standards for respectful and constructive participation.</p>
          <a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline">Read Guide →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Still Need Help?</h2>
    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6">Our support team is available Monday through Friday, 9am to 5pm EST.</p>
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="mailto:support@genderbase.org" class="btn btn-primary">Email Support</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline">View Support Hours</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
